<figureCitation id="0D9C2A67FFF905618DBFF80BE04F1394" box="[1259,1358,1992,2017]" captionStart="FIGURE 134" captionStartId="45.[151,250,1859,1881]" captionTargetBox="[153,1431,697,1834]" captionTargetId="figure@45.[151,1436,693,1837]" captionTargetPageId="45" captionText="FIGURE 134. A–C. Merosargus apicalis, male, holotype [PAN]. A. Habitus, dorsal. B. Habitus, lateral. C. Head, frontal view. D. Labels." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2614873/files/figure.png" pageId="45" pageNumber="496">Fig. 134</figureCitation>
